{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
    "name": "Lav60 - Security API (report_read)",
    "description": "Collection para consumir a Security API da Lavanderia 60 Minutos usando OAuth2 Client Credentials com escopo `report_read`.\n\n## Fluxo recomendado\n1. Configure as variáveis da collection (`client_id`, `client_secret`, etc.).\n2. Execute **OAuth2 - Obter Access Token**.\n3. O token é salvo automaticamente em `access_token`.\n4. Chame os endpoints protegidos de relatório.\n\n## Ambientes\n- **Staging:** `https://staging.lavanderia60minutos.com.br`\n- **Produção:** ajuste `base_url` conforme credencial fornecida.\n\nDocumentação: `apiclients.md`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "serverUrl",
      "value": "http://127.0.0.1:3100"
    },
    {
      "key": "client_id",
      "value": "SEU_CLIENT_ID",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "client_secret",
      "value": "SEU_CLIENT_SECRET",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "scope",
      "value": "report_read",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "access_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "storeCode",
      "value": "pb05"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Autenticação",
      "description": "Endpoints para obter e gerenciar o access token OAuth2.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "OAuth2 - Obter Access Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', json.access_token);",
                  "    pm.test('Token obtido com sucesso', function () {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.access_token).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty;",
                  "        pm.expect(json.token_type).to.eql('Bearer');",
                  "    });",
                  "    pm.test('Escopo retornado contém report_read', function () {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.scope).to.include('report_read');",
                  "    });",
                  "    console.log('access_token salvo na variável da collection. Expira em', json.expires_in, 'segundos.');",
                  "} else {",
                  "    pm.test('Falha ao obter token - verifique client_id, client_secret e escopo', function () {",
                  "        pm.expect.fail('Status: ' + pm.response.code + ' - ' + pm.response.text());",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                {
                  "key": "grant_type",
                  "value": "client_credentials",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "client_id",
                  "value": "{{client_id}}",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "client_secret",
                  "value": "{{client_secret}}",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "scope",
                  "value": "{{scope}}",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{serverUrl}}/totem/oauth/token",
              "host": [
                "{{serverUrl}}/totem"
              ],
              "path": [
                "oauth",
                "token"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Solicita um access token via fluxo OAuth2 **client_credentials**.\n\n**Pré-requisitos:**\n- Security API cadastrada e ativa no painel\n- Escopo `report_read` habilitado para a credencial\n\n**Resposta de sucesso (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"access_token\": \"eyJ...\",\n  \"token_type\": \"Bearer\",\n  \"expires_in\": 7200,\n  \"scope\": \"report_read\",\n  \"created_at\": 1720610000\n}\n```\n\nO token é salvo automaticamente na variável `access_token` da collection."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Relatórios (report_read)",
      "description": "Endpoints protegidos que exigem `Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}` e escopo `report_read`.",
      "auth": {
        "type": "bearer",
        "bearer": [
          {
            "key": "token",
            "value": "{{access_token}}",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ]
      },
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Customers",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status code é 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 401) {",
                  "    console.warn('401: Token ausente, inválido ou expirado. Execute OAuth2 - Obter Access Token.');",
                  "}",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 403) {",
                  "    console.warn('403: Token sem escopo report_read. Revise escopos da Security API.');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{access_token}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{serverUrl}}/totem/api/v1/reports/customers",
              "host": [
                "{{serverUrl}}/totem"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "reports",
                "customers"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Relatório de **clientes**.\n\nRequer Bearer token com escopo `report_read`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
